             sworn. - I am a breeches-maker, I saw the prisoner come out of Mrs. Weston's house, I lodged in the house; I followed her, and found her with the cloak and apron upon her; I took them from the prisoner, and gave them to Mrs. Weston, she delivered them to the officer.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18000528-51-person550">
                  CHARLES 
                  BUTLER
